== ATB System ==

Each character has a time gauge that fills based on Speed stat.

{| class="wikitable"
! Stat !! Effect
|-
| Speed || Determines gauge fill rate
|-
| Haste || Doubles fill rate
|-
| Slow || Halves fill rate
|}

